'''惠恕仁'''（{{lang-en|Surangel S. Whipps Jr.}}；{{bd|1968年|8月9日}}）<ref name="palau2020candidates">{{Cite web|title=Four candidates seek the presidency in Palau elections in 2020|url=https://www.mbjguam.com/2020/01/20/four-candidates-seek-the-presidency-in-palau-elections-in-2020/|date=2020-01-20|accessdate=2021-03-28|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128134149/https://www.mbjguam.com/2020/01/20/four-candidates-seek-the-presidency-in-palau-elections-in-2020/|dead-url=no}}</ref>是[[帛琉|帛琉]]政治人物和商人，2021年1月20日就任第10任[[帛琉總統|帛琉總統]]<ref name=":0">{{cite news |title=Surangel Whipps Jr to be Palau's new president |url=https://www.rnz.co.nz/international/pacific-news/429990/surangel-whipps-jr-to-be-palau-s-new-president |access-date=2020-11-06 |agency=[[新西蘭國家廣播電台|RNZ]] |date=2020-11-06 |archive-date=2020-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201105223844/https://www.rnz.co.nz/international/pacific-news/429990/surangel-whipps-jr-to-be-palau-s-new-president |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/jan/18/palaus-new-president-vows-to-stand-up-to-bully-china|title=Palau’s new president vows to stand up to ‘bully’ China|date=2021-01-18|via=theguardian.com|accessdate=2021-03-28|archive-date=2021-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216163818/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/jan/18/palaus-new-president-vows-to-stand-up-to-bully-china|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/jan/18/palaus-new-president-vows-to-stand-up-to-bully-china |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2021-03-28 |archive-date=2021-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216163818/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/jan/18/palaus-new-president-vows-to-stand-up-to-bully-china |dead-url=no }}</ref>，曾於2008年至2016年期間擔任參議員<ref name=":0" />。<!-- He is from [[雅龐|Ngatpang]] state, Republic of Palau.{{Citation needed|date=November 2020}}-->

== 早年生活 ==
惠恕仁生於[[美國|美國]][[馬里蘭州|馬里蘭州]][[巴爾的摩|巴爾的摩]]<ref name="maryland">{{cite web|url=https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=f2ve2AmBf8o |title=TFB Interview: Surangel Whipps Jr. from Palau - YouTube |publisher=M.youtube.com |access-date=2020-05-02}}</ref>，父親是{{tsl|en|Surangel Whipps|蘇朗高·惠普士}}，而母親在馬里蘭州出生<ref name="maryland" />，是家中四個孩子的老大。他4歲那年全家移民到帛琉，惠恕仁總統出生在一個幸福的家庭，度過了一個快樂的童年，他的家庭經營一家海鮮餐館，售賣每天的漁獲，也會帶游客去游覽當地景色。

惠氏先後在[[安得烈大學|安得烈大學]]和[[加利福尼亚大学洛杉矶分校|加州大學洛杉磯分校]]以工商管理及經濟學士和[[工商管理碩士|工商管理碩士]]畢業<ref>{{Cite web|title=Palau National Congress - Senators|url=http://www.palauoek.com/?page_id=19|dead-url=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304195602/http://www.palauoek.com/?page_id=19|archive-date=2016-03-04|access-date=2020-11-08|website=Palau National Congress}}</ref>，亦曾經營一間帛琉連鎖超級市場集團<ref name=":1">{{Cite news|last=Carreon|first=Bernadette|date=2021-01-18|title=Palau's new president vows to stand up to 'bully' China|language=en-GB|work=The Guardian|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/jan/18/palaus-new-president-vows-to-stand-up-to-bully-china|access-date=2021-02-11|issn=0261-3077|archive-date=2021-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216163818/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/jan/18/palaus-new-president-vows-to-stand-up-to-bully-china|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 政治生涯 ==
[[2016年帛琉大選|2016年帛琉大選]]時，惠恕仁挑戰現任總統、他的舅岳父[[小湯米·雷蒙傑索|小湯米·雷蒙傑索]]<ref name="independent">{{cite news|title=Palau island election: Brothers-in-law vying for presidency|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/australasia/palau-election-surangel-whipps-jr-tommy-remengesa-a7388551.html|work=[[獨立報|The Independent]]|date=2016-10-31|access-date=2016-11-05|archive-date=2016-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161105230555/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/australasia/palau-election-surangel-whipps-jr-tommy-remengesa-a7388551.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最終惠氏得4,854票，不敵對手的5,109票<ref name="gdp">{{cite news|first=Bernadette H.|last=Carreon|title=Palau election too close to call, Results to be decided by overseas ballots|url=http://www.postguam.com/sunday_post/palau-election-too-close-to-call/article_5ae76d46-a24d-11e6-b77d-b7b2cbab0571.html|work={{tsl|en|Guam Daily Post||Guam Daily Post}}|date=2016-11-06|access-date=2016-11-06|archive-date=2019-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191015130437/https://www.postguam.com/sunday_post/palau-election-too-close-to-call/article_5ae76d46-a24d-11e6-b77d-b7b2cbab0571.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

{{tsl|en|2020 Palauan presidential election|2020年帛琉總統選舉|2020年總統選舉}}，惠恕仁再次參選，挑戰時任副總統{{tsl|en|Raynold Oilouch|歐宜樓}}<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{cite news |last1=Carreon |first1=Bernadette |title=Palauans vote on new political era |url=https://www.rnz.co.nz/international/pacific-news/429766/palauans-vote-on-new-political-era |access-date=2020-11-03 |agency=[[新西蘭國家廣播電台|RNZ]] |date=2020-11-03 |archive-date=2020-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118100848/https://www.rnz.co.nz/international/pacific-news/429766/palauans-vote-on-new-political-era |dead-url=no }}</ref>，支持稅務改革及增加政府收入途徑<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-11-06|title=Surangel Whipps Jr to be Palau's new president|url=https://www.rnz.co.nz/international/pacific-news/429990/surangel-whipps-jr-to-be-palau-s-new-president|access-date=2021-02-11|website=RNZ|language=en-nz|archive-date=2020-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201105223844/https://www.rnz.co.nz/international/pacific-news/429990/surangel-whipps-jr-to-be-palau-s-new-president|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他提出分發[[2019冠狀病毒病疫苗|2019冠狀病毒病疫苗]]予帛琉市民，尤其是醫護<ref>{{Cite web|title=President Surangel Whipps, Jr. of Palau|url=https://www.bridgingbordersproject.com/episodes/palau|access-date=2021-02-11|website=Bridging Borders|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127022715/https://www.bridgingbordersproject.com/episodes/palau|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2021年3月28日，惠恕仁訪問[[中華民國|中華民國]]，是[[2019冠狀病毒病臺灣疫情|2019冠狀病毒病臺灣疫情]]爆發後首位到訪該國的國家元首<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=帛琉總統惠恕仁率團抵台 美國駐帛琉大使隨行|url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202103285004.aspx|accessdate=2021-03-28|location=桃園|author=吳睿騏|editor=李錫璋|date=2021-03-28|work=中央通訊社|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2021-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210328080948/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202103285004.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==個人生活==
惠恕仁總統已婚，有4個孩子，總統和夫人在悠閑的時候總會抽出時間陪伴家人，還會和孩子打球釣魚潛水。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.palaugov.pw/executive-branch/president/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2022-04-22 |archive-date=2022-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220619113205/https://www.palaugov.pw/executive-branch/president/ }}</ref>
